f=Engineering/nova/custom/app-store-release-discipline/assets/app-release-checklist.md · h1:App Store Release Checklist nova/app-store-release-discipline=mobile_active. Mobile can't instantly roll back staged rollout rollback. conservative web design. Store specifics dated playbook. · h2:Gate: mobile_active=mobile_active true (else dormant; route mia) · h2:Pre-submission (blocking)=quinn GATE PASS (quality) charter clean (security), mobile-verification REAL devices iOS Android (simulator lies), Crash-free target device matrix, Feature-flag kill-switch wired any risky new feature (raj real safety net) · h2:Store guidelines=iOS review guidelines: privacy labels, permission justifications, payment rules, Android policy: data safety, permissions, target API level, Rejection risks reviewed (rejection lost days) · h2:Versioning & submission=Build/version bumped correctly; release notes written, Phased staged release configured, Signing: performed OPERATOR (agent never holds signing keys) · h2:Staged rollout (mobile's rollback substitute)=watch crash-free rate review sentiment, 10% watch, 100% watch, Any degradation HALT rollout, forward-fix, feature-flag disable, expedited review severe · h2:Post-release=Crash-free rate baseline ops) reviews monitored, Forward-fix path confirmed (rollback weak; flag expedited review plan)